                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Leishman</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Pera</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-08-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 2, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Leishman reports that the minister for foreign affairs communicated to him
                    last night that the Sultan would be unable to give the promised reply before
                    next Thursday, because the council of ministers had not yet concluded its
                    report. Mr. Leishman expects that a definite decision will be reached this
                    week.)</p>
            </div>
